description: Byggma ASA, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and supplies building materials in Norway, the United Kingdom, Sweden, Finland, Denmark, and internationally. It operates through Panels, Beams, Windows, and Lighting segments. The company offers pre-painted ceilings and wall panels under the Huntonit brand; I-beams for use in ceilings, walls, and floors for wood-based buildings under the Masonite brand; and particle boards, boards, and structural panels for use in buildings, interior ceilings, and wall panels under the Forestia brand. It also provides doors and windows for new buildings, extensions, and rehabilitations under the Uldal brand; and a range of lighting products, such as decorative home lighting, lampshades, and professional functional lighting products under the Aneta Lighting brand. In addition, the company develops, manufactures, and distributes MDF panels for walls, ceilings, bathrooms, and kitchens under the Smartpanel brand. It sells its products through dealers and electrical wholesalers. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Vennesla, Norway. Byggma ASA is a subsidiary of Investor As.
